OL,6,FBadenoch's comments on Sunday sparked
OL,7,Fa backlash after she appeared to
OL,8,Fcriticise statutory maternity pay,
OL,9,Fsaying the government is doing "too
OL,10,Fmuch".
OL,12,FShe has since appeared to row back on
OL,13,Fher remarks, posting on X that she
OL,14,Fdoes support maternity pay.
OL,16,FShe wrote: "Contrary to what some have
OL,17,Fsaid, I clearly said the burden of
OL,18,Fregulation on businesses had gone too
OL,19,Ffar... of course I believe in
OL,20,Fmaternity pay! Watch the clip for the
OL,21,Ftruth."
