OL,6,FIt provides 90% of a person's salary
OL,7,Ffor six weeks, and then whichever is
OL,8,Flower of 90% of their salary or
OL,9,F#184.03 per week for the next 33
OL,10,Fweeks, and the payment is liable for
OL,11,Fincome tax and national insurance.
