OL,14,Fgroup Pregnant Then Screwed, said it
OL,15,Fis "absolute nonsense" to suggest
OL,16,Fbusinesses are closing because of
OL,17,Fstatutory maternity pay because they
OL,18,Fare able to recoup the cost from HMRC.
